<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000001
00:01:38.100 --> 00:01:39.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[wheels rattling]
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000002
00:01:42.940 --> 00:01:44.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts]
-Huh.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:47.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000004
00:01:48.320 --> 00:01:49.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You three seem close.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:51.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, how long have
you been traveling together?</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:51.700 --> 00:01:54.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, um...well...</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:54.410 --> 00:01:56.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My travels
with Mistress Frieren</b></Default>

c0000008
00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:57.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>began four years ago,</b></Default>

c0000009
00:01:57.620 --> 00:01:58.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I've known her longer.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:01:59.490 --> 00:02:01.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been about a year for me.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:02.710 --> 00:02:03.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:04.460 --> 00:02:05.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makes sense.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:05.790 --> 00:02:10.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:13.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Y'know, there's still something
this party lacks.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:15.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What?
-Wanna take a guess?</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:16.550 --> 00:02:17.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's see.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:19.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've got our front-liner,
a decent priest,</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:20.020 --> 00:02:21.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and a near surplus of mages.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:22.100 --> 00:02:23.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could you mean a thief?</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:23.560 --> 00:02:25.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone to out-swindle
the mimics</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:25.230 --> 00:02:26.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she's always falling for?</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:27.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FRIEREN] Yay!
-[FERN] [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:27.560 --> 00:02:29.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thuds]
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:30.690 --> 00:02:31.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When it comes
to treasure chests,</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:31.900 --> 00:02:33.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the reward always
outweighs the risk.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:34.570 --> 00:02:36.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[SEIN] No.
-Huh.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:36.530 --> 00:02:38.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] What we lack
is something even more vital.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:39.830 --> 00:02:41.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's a nice-looking
older lady!</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:41.950 --> 00:02:43.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Most parties won't even
leave town</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:43.370 --> 00:02:44.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until they've found a broad!</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:44.410 --> 00:02:47.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the way! Or else
you're vixen-less like us!</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:47.840 --> 00:02:49.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Is that right?</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:50.130 --> 00:02:52.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on.
Don't forget about Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:02:52.340 --> 00:02:55.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's more of an elderly child
than a lady.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:02:55.220 --> 00:02:56.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
He looks so distraught.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:02:56.760 --> 00:02:58.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
My apologies.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:02:58.100 --> 00:02:59.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...hey!</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:00.100 --> 00:03:02.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can finally see
the next village.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:03.940 --> 00:03:06.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:10.690 --> 00:03:11.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:20.030 --> 00:03:21.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
They're still breathing.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:21.450 --> 00:03:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Same here.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:24.370 --> 00:03:26.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the deal
with this place?</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:27.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why'd they all fall asleep?</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:27.540 --> 00:03:30.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:30.130 --> 00:03:32.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I say we move along
to the next village.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:32.380 --> 00:03:33.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This smells like trouble.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:36.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even for you, that's cold.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:36.470 --> 00:03:37.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was only teasing.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:39.510 --> 00:03:40.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A curse, no doubt.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:41.060 --> 00:03:42.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought as much.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:42.390 --> 00:03:43.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a headache.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:44.810 --> 00:03:47.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This may sound dumb,
but what even is a curse?</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:48.190 --> 00:03:51.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Among the spells utilized
by monsters and demons</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:51.570 --> 00:03:53.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are those that
put people to sleep</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:53.190 --> 00:03:55.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-or turn them into stone.
-[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:55.320 --> 00:03:56.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Those whose
mysteries humankind</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:57.070 --> 00:03:59.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is yet to unravel
are what we call curses.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:03:59.700 --> 00:04:01.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A placeholder for the unknown.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:02.740 --> 00:04:05.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Humanity's magic can't explain
the principles behind them</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:05.700 --> 00:04:07.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-or how to lift them.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:07.660 --> 00:04:10.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does that mean it's already
too late to save these people?</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:10.420 --> 00:04:13.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is only the magic of man
that faces such an impasse.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:14.550 --> 00:04:16.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The magic of the Goddess
that priests use</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:16.550 --> 00:04:17.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is a different story.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:18.840 --> 00:04:21.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dispelling curses has long been
the business of the clergy.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:23.390 --> 00:04:25.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Sein?
Suppose you can help them?</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:26.850 --> 00:04:27.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't rush me.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:28.100 --> 00:04:30.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need to determine the type
and source of this thing.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:34.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:34.690 --> 00:04:36.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought magic was magic.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:36.530 --> 00:04:38.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What makes
the Goddess' so unique?</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:38.950 --> 00:04:40.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The magic of the Goddess
is recorded</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:40.740 --> 00:04:42.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in holy scriptures, you see.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:44.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only those who own them
can wield it.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:45.740 --> 00:04:47.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Much like the demons' magic,</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:47.250 --> 00:04:49.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the principles behind the bulk
of it aren't understood.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:50.880 --> 00:04:53.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, it's not the sort of thing
that holds my interest.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:53.790 --> 00:04:54.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?!</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:57.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That, and it's incredibly
difficult to use</b></Default>

c0000082
00:04:57.420 --> 00:04:59.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>unless you're born
with a certain knack.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:04:59.340 --> 00:05:00.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Hm.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:00.510 --> 00:05:02.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
That same predisposition comes</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:02.220 --> 00:05:04.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with an increased resistance
to curses.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:05.010 --> 00:05:06.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's what
the faithful bunch call</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:08.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the blessing of the Goddess,</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:08.560 --> 00:05:10.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it's the reason
this sleepy spell</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:10.350 --> 00:05:11.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>won't affect our priest.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:12.770 --> 00:05:14.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So not even
a mage at your level</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:14.560 --> 00:05:16.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can really defend
against curses?</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:19.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We mages can't detect them,
let alone defend against them.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:20.150 --> 00:05:21.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I do feel that
I am under attack</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:22.070 --> 00:05:23.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for some reason.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I can conclude
that this place</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:24.780 --> 00:05:26.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is still under the power
of the curse.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:27.290 --> 00:05:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My soul feels itchy.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:28.660 --> 00:05:30.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't just say
scary things like that</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:30.370 --> 00:05:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and expect me not to turn
into a giant, sniveling baby!</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't a low-grade,
everyday spell</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:37.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're dealing with here.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:38.090 --> 00:05:39.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you lift it or can't you?</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:40.130 --> 00:05:41.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would need the right tools.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:44.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, it might be easier</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:44.300 --> 00:05:46.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to take out the source
than to treat its symptoms.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:49.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's coming from a monster,</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:49.310 --> 00:05:50.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I know where it is.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:05:50.980 --> 00:05:51.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:05:52.350 --> 00:05:54.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I like how you cut
to the chase.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:05:56.230 --> 00:05:57.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:05:57.570 --> 00:05:58.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Mistress Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000112
00:05:59.730 --> 00:06:00.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's Mister Stark.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:01.570 --> 00:06:04.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bird chirping]</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:04.610 --> 00:06:05.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That didn't take long.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:06.780 --> 00:06:08.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any chance you can
temporarily wake him?</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:09.580 --> 00:06:11.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told you I don't have
the proper tools.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:11.750 --> 00:06:14.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As is, I could only keep him up
for five seconds.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:14.460 --> 00:06:16.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
That's practically nothing.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:16.790 --> 00:06:19.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] In any case, it looks
like we should hurry.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:19.750 --> 00:06:26.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:29.180 --> 00:06:32.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:34.350 --> 00:06:35.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:06:35.850 --> 00:06:38.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000124
00:06:39.150 --> 00:06:40.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:41.860 --> 00:06:43.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern's out cold, too.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:43.530 --> 00:06:45.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So much for her
taking a little break.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:48.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've lost
half of our manpower.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:48.950 --> 00:06:50.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our odds are starting
to look grim.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:51.160 --> 00:06:53.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I put up a barrier.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:56.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll hide them here for now.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:57.080 --> 00:07:02.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:02.170 --> 00:07:03.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're almost there.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:03.670 --> 00:07:04.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can sense it.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:05.630 --> 00:07:06.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Good.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:06.930 --> 00:07:08.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Say, Sein?</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:08.300 --> 00:07:10.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wake me when
the monster shows up.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:11.510 --> 00:07:13.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want you fighting
that creature alone.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:14.100 --> 00:07:16.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I promise you now
that I shall defeat it.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:16.520 --> 00:07:17.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Were you not listening?</b></Default>

c0000142
00:07:17.810 --> 00:07:20.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can only give you...
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000143
00:07:21.230 --> 00:07:22.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000144
00:07:22.320 --> 00:07:24.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000145
00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't defeat it
in five seconds.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:07:26.610 --> 00:07:33.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000147
00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:36.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
So be it.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:38.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have battle magic, too.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:07:50.640 --> 00:07:57.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000150
00:07:57.690 --> 00:07:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] It's a subspecies
of chaos flower.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:00.440 --> 00:08:02.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It must be feeding
off the sleeping villagers.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:04.190 --> 00:08:06.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll sap their mana away
until it kills them.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:09.070 --> 00:08:10.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:12.450 --> 00:08:15.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Chaos flowers are known
to merge with the local flora</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:15.410 --> 00:08:17.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and branch off
into new variations.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:18.750 --> 00:08:19.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts]
-[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:21.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
Almost mirror-like.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:22.250 --> 00:08:24.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though they come
in different shapes and sizes,</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:24.840 --> 00:08:27.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they all have the same
weak spot at their core.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:27.340 --> 00:08:29.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:30.050 --> 00:08:31.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Three Spears of the Goddess!</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:33.430 --> 00:08:34.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000163
00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:41.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
What was that about?</b></Default>

c0000164
00:08:43.150 --> 00:08:44.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't think
the blasted thing</b></Default>

c0000165
00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:45.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would reflect my magic.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:08:46.900 --> 00:08:48.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unless I land
a direct hit on the core,</b></Default>

c0000167
00:08:49.490 --> 00:08:51.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the leaves can deflect
whatever I throw at it</b></Default>

c0000168
00:08:51.530 --> 00:08:52.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in any direction.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:08:53.990 --> 00:08:56.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I'm not careful,
it could hit Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:08:56.830 --> 00:08:57.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000171
00:08:58.580 --> 00:08:59.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thuds]
-[SEIN] Damn it.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:08:59.710 --> 00:09:01.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This can only get
worse from here.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:09:01.460 --> 00:09:03.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should I heed the elf's orders
and wake her?</b></Default>

c0000174
00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's the mage
from the party of heroes.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:09:06.050 --> 00:09:07.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If a spell of hers
were deflected,</b></Default>

c0000176
00:09:07.800 --> 00:09:09.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it would destroy
not only the forest,</b></Default>

c0000177
00:09:09.630 --> 00:09:11.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but the entire village with it!</b></Default>

c0000178
00:09:12.550 --> 00:09:13.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000179
00:09:13.550 --> 00:09:15.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
I'd only have five seconds.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:09:15.560 --> 00:09:17.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not enough time
to explain.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:20.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As sharp as Freiren is,
we haven't had time to develop</b></Default>

c0000182
00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:22.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>any kind of shared trust
or mutual understanding.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:09:23.150 --> 00:09:24.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't even get a read on her.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:09:25.020 --> 00:09:26.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What goes on
in that ancient head?</b></Default>

c0000185
00:09:27.190 --> 00:09:28.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000186
00:09:28.860 --> 00:09:29.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
That's right.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:31.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You might find it hard
to believe,</b></Default>

c0000188
00:09:31.990 --> 00:09:34.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I can never tell
what she's thinking.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:09:34.910 --> 00:09:36.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shared trust is a luxury,</b></Default>

c0000190
00:09:36.950 --> 00:09:39.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as in it's not something
adventurers need.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:09:39.370 --> 00:09:41.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing has to be unspoken.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:09:41.830 --> 00:09:44.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know this because
my companion Frieren</b></Default>

c0000193
00:09:44.380 --> 00:09:47.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was terrible at cultivating
mutual understanding.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:09:47.920 --> 00:09:50.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since intent couldn't be
assured with a look or a touch,</b></Default>

c0000195
00:09:51.130 --> 00:09:53.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I decided I would
trust her words.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:09:54.260 --> 00:09:56.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For example,
she swore to us all</b></Default>

c0000197
00:09:56.430 --> 00:09:58.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she would
defeat the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:09:59.060 --> 00:10:01.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though it was a bold claim,
I chose to believe her.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:10:02.940 --> 00:10:04.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
Trust her words, huh?</b></Default>

c0000200
00:10:05.860 --> 00:10:07.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000201
00:10:09.570 --> 00:10:10.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000202
00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:13.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want you fighting
that creature on your own.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:10:13.820 --> 00:10:16.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I promise you now
that I shall defeat it.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:10:16.370 --> 00:10:17.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000205
00:10:17.830 --> 00:10:19.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That face didn't look
ready to defeat anything.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:10:19.910 --> 00:10:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000207
00:10:21.040 --> 00:10:22.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever happens,
don't blame me!</b></Default>

c0000208
00:10:23.620 --> 00:10:25.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Awakening spell!</b></Default>

c0000209
00:10:26.130 --> 00:10:27.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000210
00:10:28.800 --> 00:10:31.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren! Only the core.
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000211
00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:38.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000212
00:10:44.770 --> 00:10:47.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000213
00:10:47.690 --> 00:10:48.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

c0000214
00:10:50.190 --> 00:10:51.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:10:52.030 --> 00:10:54.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Done. Simple enough.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:10:55.240 --> 00:10:58.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000217
00:10:58.660 --> 00:10:59.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000218
00:11:00.290 --> 00:11:01.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:11:01.740 --> 00:11:04.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft snoring]</b></Default>

c0000220
00:11:05.500 --> 00:11:07.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. Well, this is new.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:11:10.420 --> 00:11:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE VILLAGER 15A]
Thank you very much.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:11:12.760 --> 00:11:14.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I won't forget what
you've done for us.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:11:14.970 --> 00:11:17.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's nothing. I can assure you
we didn't do much, ma'am.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:11:17.930 --> 00:11:19.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. Hush, now.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:11:20.180 --> 00:11:22.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never been happier
to have my sleep disturbed.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:26.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000227
00:11:26.650 --> 00:11:27.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

c0000228
00:11:28.440 --> 00:11:31.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I knew our flower was
the type that reflects magic.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:11:31.530 --> 00:11:33.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I recognized it the moment
you woke me up.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:11:34.570 --> 00:11:37.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] There's no question that
you're an incredible mage.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:11:37.990 --> 00:11:39.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That might be the case,</b></Default>

c0000232
00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:41.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you're the reason
we made it out of there alive.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:11:42.410 --> 00:11:43.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you very much, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:11:46.790 --> 00:11:48.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both grunt]</b></Default>

c0000235
00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good boy.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:11:51.460 --> 00:11:53.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000237
00:11:54.090 --> 00:11:57.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000238
00:11:57.430 --> 00:11:58.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
That lady from the village</b></Default>

c0000239
00:11:58.800 --> 00:12:00.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>sure was pretty.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:12:00.720 --> 00:12:02.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
You're still on that?</b></Default>

c0000241
00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:06.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, that's Vorig, huh?</b></Default>

c0000242
00:12:06.850 --> 00:12:08.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] More importantly,
it's the midpoint</b></Default>

c0000243
00:12:08.520 --> 00:12:09.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in our journey to Auberst.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:12:10.940 --> 00:12:12.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
We're only halfway there?</b></Default>

c0000245
00:12:13.070 --> 00:12:14.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This really is a long journey.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:12:15.900 --> 00:12:17.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
While we're here, let's drop in</b></Default>

c0000247
00:12:17.400 --> 00:12:18.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and replenish our supplies.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:12:18.700 --> 00:12:20.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, Mistress Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000249
00:12:20.740 --> 00:12:22.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hate to be
the bearer of bad news,</b></Default>

c0000250
00:12:22.780 --> 00:12:24.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but our funds are--</b></Default>

c0000251
00:12:24.120 --> 00:12:25.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORDEN]
Hey, you there.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:12:25.540 --> 00:12:26.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm? What now?</b></Default>

c0000253
00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:31.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That looks like
a noble's carriage.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:12:33.090 --> 00:12:34.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000255
00:12:34.510 --> 00:12:36.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Excuse you! What is going on?</b></Default>

c0000256
00:12:37.340 --> 00:12:38.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He has a good physique.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:12:38.800 --> 00:12:40.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His looks aren't bad, either.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:12:40.720 --> 00:12:42.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Get in.
I'll take you to my mansion.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:12:43.970 --> 00:12:47.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Does anybody care to explain?</b></Default>

c0000260
00:12:53.360 --> 00:12:54.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who are you, lad?</b></Default>

c0000261
00:12:55.230 --> 00:12:56.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
The name is Stark.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:12:56.530 --> 00:12:57.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lord Orden, sir?</b></Default>

c0000263
00:12:57.900 --> 00:12:59.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You cannot hold us
without reason.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:12:59.860 --> 00:13:01.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need no introduction, I see.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:13:02.160 --> 00:13:03.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This mansion is home
to the Ordens,</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:03.870 --> 00:13:06.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>one of the Three Great Families
of the northern lands.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:09.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your grandfather?
He was pushy, too.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:13:09.620 --> 00:13:12.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know what nonsense
you're trying to engage me in,</b></Default>

c0000269
00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'm preoccupied
at the moment.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:13:14.790 --> 00:13:16.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stark and I need
to have a word.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:13:16.590 --> 00:13:19.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you can talk to my warrior,
you can talk to me.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:13:21.180 --> 00:13:22.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORDEN]
Tell me, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:13:22.470 --> 00:13:23.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you need
your mommy's permission</b></Default>

c0000274
00:13:23.890 --> 00:13:24.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to have a conversation?</b></Default>

c0000275
00:13:25.760 --> 00:13:27.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>C'mon, don't fight.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:13:28.020 --> 00:13:29.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a job for you,</b></Default>

c0000277
00:13:29.730 --> 00:13:30.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I will pay you well.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:13:31.270 --> 00:13:33.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. No chance.
We're leaving, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:13:33.860 --> 00:13:35.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:13:35.610 --> 00:13:36.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[coins clinking]</b></Default>

c0000281
00:13:39.990 --> 00:13:41.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's with the copper?</b></Default>

c0000282
00:13:41.860 --> 00:13:43.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the remainder
of our funds.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:13:45.910 --> 00:13:47.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose that
at the very least</b></Default>

c0000284
00:13:47.580 --> 00:13:48.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can hear you out.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:13:48.910 --> 00:13:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lucky me.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:13:53.880 --> 00:13:56.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Stark.
From where do you hail?</b></Default>

c0000287
00:13:57.460 --> 00:14:00.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm from a warrior village
in the Klee region, sir.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:14:00.550 --> 00:14:01.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORDEN]
I know the place.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:14:02.010 --> 00:14:04.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My family line originates
from the very same region.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:14:05.800 --> 00:14:06.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000291
00:14:10.350 --> 00:14:11.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORDEN]
My eldest son, Wirt.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:14:13.060 --> 00:14:16.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He is a hero of this city,
and the heir to my title.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:14:17.070 --> 00:14:19.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] He looks like you,
Mister Stark.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:14:19.860 --> 00:14:21.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORDEN]
Indeed he does.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:14:21.700 --> 00:14:23.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we changed you
and cleaned you up,</b></Default>

c0000296
00:14:23.490 --> 00:14:26.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only a close family member
could discern the difference.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:14:26.740 --> 00:14:29.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a feeling that's going
to play into your job offer.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:14:30.790 --> 00:14:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About a month ago now,</b></Default>

c0000299
00:14:32.410 --> 00:14:34.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we took a vast army
of demons on head-to-head.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:14:35.250 --> 00:14:37.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My son lost his life
on the battlefield.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:14:38.040 --> 00:14:40.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He and the enemy commander
killed each other.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:14:41.590 --> 00:14:44.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only silver lining,
if you could call it as much,</b></Default>

c0000303
00:14:44.220 --> 00:14:46.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is that it happened
in a large-scale melee.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:49.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Very few know he's dead.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:14:49.770 --> 00:14:53.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gabel is aware, as well as
some of my most trusted men.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:14:53.270 --> 00:14:56.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000307
00:14:56.980 --> 00:14:59.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what is it that you're
planning to make Stark do?</b></Default>

c0000308
00:14:59.780 --> 00:15:02.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000309
00:15:02.440 --> 00:15:04.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vorig is a powerful
fortress city,</b></Default>

c0000310
00:15:04.660 --> 00:15:06.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a key player
in this region's defense.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:15:07.240 --> 00:15:09.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until we can rebuild
the forces we lost,</b></Default>

c0000312
00:15:09.660 --> 00:15:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can't allow morale to slip.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:15:12.620 --> 00:15:15.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you want to cover up
your son's death until then?</b></Default>

c0000314
00:15:16.420 --> 00:15:17.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORDEN]
Three months from now,</b></Default>

c0000315
00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:20.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all of the area's
most influential figures</b></Default>

c0000316
00:15:20.130 --> 00:15:21.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will gather at a soiree.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:15:21.880 --> 00:15:24.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll show them there
that Wirt is alive and well.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:15:25.220 --> 00:15:26.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And our reward?</b></Default>

c0000319
00:15:26.510 --> 00:15:28.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will give you
10 Strahl gold coins.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:15:29.390 --> 00:15:32.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That would be three meals a day
for an entire year plus snacks.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:15:32.390 --> 00:15:33.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sweeten it with a grimoire.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:15:34.270 --> 00:15:35.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can have your pick
of the library</b></Default>

c0000323
00:15:35.890 --> 00:15:37.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after our work is done.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:15:37.350 --> 00:15:39.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One problem! I'm not your guy.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:15:39.650 --> 00:15:41.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Folks aren't gonna miss
the big scar on my forehead.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:15:42.110 --> 00:15:44.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The people believe Wirt
is currently recovering</b></Default>

c0000327
00:15:44.530 --> 00:15:46.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from damage taken in combat.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:15:46.780 --> 00:15:48.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's an honorable
battle scar.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:15:49.240 --> 00:15:50.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

c0000330
00:15:51.410 --> 00:15:53.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Stark.
We need the money.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:15:54.370 --> 00:15:55.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're pathetic.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:15:56.370 --> 00:15:59.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gabel? I leave the boy's
etiquette training to you.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:16:00.130 --> 00:16:07.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000334
00:16:26.240 --> 00:16:27.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Stark.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:16:27.450 --> 00:16:29.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How is etiquette training
coming along?</b></Default>

c0000336
00:16:29.700 --> 00:16:31.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's slowly killing me.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:16:31.530 --> 00:16:38.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000338
00:16:39.580 --> 00:16:40.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think?</b></Default>

c0000339
00:16:42.540 --> 00:16:43.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Doesn't suit you.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:16:44.050 --> 00:16:45.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Typical.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:16:45.670 --> 00:16:48.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Farewell, my lady.
I must get some air.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:16:56.180 --> 00:16:57.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Lord Orden.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:16:59.770 --> 00:17:01.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Haven't I told you
a hundred times</b></Default>

c0000344
00:17:01.480 --> 00:17:02.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to call me Father?</b></Default>

c0000345
00:17:02.940 --> 00:17:05.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You never know whose
prying eyes could be upon us.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:17:05.690 --> 00:17:07.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aren't you being
a little bit cold?</b></Default>

c0000347
00:17:08.570 --> 00:17:11.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's only been two months since
your actual son passed away.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:11.910 --> 00:17:13.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All that I have done
has been in accordance</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:13.700 --> 00:17:15.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with my son's final wishes.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:15.870 --> 00:17:17.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I even had
another double prepared.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:17:19.040 --> 00:17:21.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He didn't look as much like
him as you do, though.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:26.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Trust me, it's not as if I
enjoy this cruel charade.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:17:27.300 --> 00:17:28.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:17:29.090 --> 00:17:30.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ORDEN]
But it's what my son wanted.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:17:32.260 --> 00:17:33.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So cooperate, would you?</b></Default>

c0000356
00:17:36.680 --> 00:17:38.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not too big
on the people skills, huh?</b></Default>

c0000357
00:17:40.520 --> 00:17:42.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000358
00:17:43.730 --> 00:17:46.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stand tall.
Don't shrink yourself, Mut.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:17:46.860 --> 00:17:48.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, Father. Of course.
[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000360
00:17:49.400 --> 00:17:50.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's my second son, Mut.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:17:51.530 --> 00:17:53.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Despite the fact he's to be
my heir now,</b></Default>

c0000362
00:17:53.620 --> 00:17:55.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he shows little improvement.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:17:55.870 --> 00:17:57.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, of course,
there's your brother,</b></Default>

c0000364
00:17:58.000 --> 00:17:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>our family's great shame.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:18:01.500 --> 00:18:04.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000366
00:18:04.080 --> 00:18:06.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Having skill with a sword
affects one's posture.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:09.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall teach you the technique
of the Orden family.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:18:09.550 --> 00:18:14.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000369
00:18:14.890 --> 00:18:15.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000370
00:18:16.050 --> 00:18:21.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000371
00:18:21.600 --> 00:18:22.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh.
-[ORDEN] It's all right.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:18:22.890 --> 00:18:25.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ORDEN] Take deep breaths.
-[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000373
00:18:25.980 --> 00:18:28.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't your village.
You're safe to learn here.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:18:31.360 --> 00:18:34.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I realize he's still a kid,
but what do you think of Mut?</b></Default>

c0000375
00:18:34.700 --> 00:18:36.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He doesn't have
his brother's talent.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:18:38.410 --> 00:18:39.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But he's a hard worker.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:18:40.290 --> 00:18:41.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-Time and effort</b></Default>

c0000378
00:18:41.710 --> 00:18:43.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are investments
that always pay off.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:18:44.500 --> 00:18:46.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once he's grown,
he'll be a far stronger knight</b></Default>

c0000380
00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:48.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than I ever was.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:18:48.380 --> 00:18:49.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gotcha.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:18:50.550 --> 00:18:52.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should really tell that
to Mut instead of me.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:18:53.220 --> 00:18:54.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I tell him all the time.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:18:55.300 --> 00:18:58.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now it's gone to his head,
and he refuses to get better.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:18:58.350 --> 00:18:59.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000386
00:18:59.930 --> 00:19:01.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a whole
different kind of problem.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:19:02.520 --> 00:19:03.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000388
00:19:04.140 --> 00:19:06.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're saying I have to learn
all that etiquette stuff, too?</b></Default>

c0000389
00:19:07.020 --> 00:19:08.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, it is a soiree.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:19:08.690 --> 00:19:10.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you really expect
a man of his age</b></Default>

c0000391
00:19:10.650 --> 00:19:12.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to attend such a function
on his own?</b></Default>

c0000392
00:19:12.860 --> 00:19:13.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:19:14.240 --> 00:19:17.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose his mommy could
always escort him instead.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:19:18.990 --> 00:19:20.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good luck, Fern.
[chomps]</b></Default>

c0000395
00:19:21.580 --> 00:19:22.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:19:23.540 --> 00:19:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000397
00:19:46.270 --> 00:19:48.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wheels rattling]</b></Default>

c0000398
00:19:48.770 --> 00:19:51.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all laughing]</b></Default>

c0000399
00:19:51.480 --> 00:19:53.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000400
00:19:54.030 --> 00:19:56.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This past month has been
nothing short of torture.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:19:57.820 --> 00:19:59.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But anything
for the money, right?</b></Default>

c0000402
00:20:00.320 --> 00:20:01.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry about all that.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:20:01.910 --> 00:20:08.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:11.630 --> 00:20:13.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've been
practicing this for ages.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:13.880 --> 00:20:15.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We might as well.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:16.470 --> 00:20:18.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It still doesn't suit you,
you know.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:18.590 --> 00:20:25.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000408
00:21:28.960 --> 00:21:30.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you like
to dance, as well?</b></Default>

c0000409
00:21:31.540 --> 00:21:33.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like to eat.
[chomps]</b></Default>

c0000410
00:21:35.380 --> 00:21:36.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fair enough.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:21:41.010 --> 00:21:42.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If not for this damn injury,</b></Default>

c0000412
00:21:43.180 --> 00:21:45.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would've been in the vanguard
alongside him.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:21:46.890 --> 00:21:49.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps then,
Wirt would still be with us.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:21:49.850 --> 00:21:50.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Milord.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:21:51.140 --> 00:21:52.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000416
00:21:52.350 --> 00:21:54.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000417
00:21:55.230 --> 00:21:57.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks like
the soiree's wrapping up.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:21:58.190 --> 00:21:59.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000419
00:21:59.950 --> 00:22:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've completed
your work with us.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:22:02.110 --> 00:22:05.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gabel? See to it
Frieren gets her reward.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:08.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000422
00:22:09.830 --> 00:22:11.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

c0000423
00:22:13.580 --> 00:22:16.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've found you're
far more powerful a warrior</b></Default>

c0000424
00:22:16.710 --> 00:22:18.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than you appear
at first glance.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:22:19.090 --> 00:22:20.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you ever need
a place to stay...</b></Default>

c0000426
00:22:20.710 --> 00:22:23.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry, sir,
but I can't replace your son.</b></Default>

c0000427
00:22:24.140 --> 00:22:25.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, you can't.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:22:26.430 --> 00:22:29.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No more than I could ever
replace your father.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:22:30.310 --> 00:22:32.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you don't have
a home to return to.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:22:33.100 --> 00:22:35.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The warrior village
of the Klee region</b></Default>

c0000431
00:22:35.110 --> 00:22:36.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was destroyed by demons.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:22:37.150 --> 00:22:38.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm certain of that much.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:22:40.900 --> 00:22:42.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My son and I
parted ways in anger,</b></Default>

c0000434
00:22:43.950 --> 00:22:45.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all due to some petty argument.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:22:46.950 --> 00:22:48.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I worked myself
into a fit of rage</b></Default>

c0000436
00:22:49.040 --> 00:22:51.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and told him I never wanted
to see his face again.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:22:53.210 --> 00:22:54.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't mean one bit of it.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:22:55.960 --> 00:22:58.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000439
00:22:59.210 --> 00:23:02.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I first came upon you,
I mistook you for a miracle.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:23:02.760 --> 00:23:06.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000441
00:23:06.260 --> 00:23:08.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's all the more reason
I can't stay here.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:23:10.390 --> 00:23:13.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I said things I didn't mean
and parted in anger, too.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:23:14.020 --> 00:23:15.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With the man who raised me.</b></Default>

c0000444
00:23:16.650 --> 00:23:18.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So now, my hope is
to make things right</b></Default>

c0000445
00:23:19.070 --> 00:23:21.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by bringing him back
stories of my travels.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:23:23.820 --> 00:23:24.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wish you well.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:23:25.240 --> 00:23:28.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000448
00:23:28.570 --> 00:23:29.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000449
00:23:30.780 --> 00:23:33.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should I rule out Grimoire Y
or Grimoire Z?</b></Default>

c0000450
00:23:34.080 --> 00:23:35.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:23:35.330 --> 00:23:37.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've been deciding
for half a day.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:23:38.460 --> 00:23:40.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're distressing
Mister Gabel.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:23:40.960 --> 00:23:42.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please hurry.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:23:42.960 --> 00:23:45.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look. You drained
the poor man's life force.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:23:46.840 --> 00:23:48.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They say
it'll still be some time</b></Default>

c0000456
00:23:48.470 --> 00:23:50.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before their troops are back
to what they were.</b></Default>

c0000457
00:23:52.930 --> 00:23:53.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000458
00:23:54.180 --> 00:23:55.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's up?</b></Default>

c0000459
00:23:55.430 --> 00:23:56.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?!</b></Default>

c0000460
00:23:57.560 --> 00:23:58.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:24:02.360 --> 00:24:05.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At the very least, he won't
have to worry about his heir.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:24:06.860 --> 00:24:07.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000463
00:24:08.070 --> 00:24:15.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000464
00:24:16.210 --> 00:24:17.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000465
00:24:21.090 --> 00:24:22.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
Forgotten heroes, huh?</b></Default>

c0000466
00:24:23.500 --> 00:24:24.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[STARK] More like decrepit.
-[FERN] So</b></Default>

c0000467
00:24:24.590 --> 00:24:26.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he's always been lonely then.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:24:26.090 --> 00:24:27.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VOLL]
Humans develop quickly.</b></Default>

c0000469
00:24:28.050 --> 00:24:29.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] He's
a long-lived friend of mine.</b></Default>

